{"tid":1381023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 美國停止向香港警方售賣群眾管理工具","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:15.000Z","uid":192943,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f57a59ab40d5a534667b86c5fced153d41ff49","tid":1381023,"uid":192943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"sor做左標題黨，唔做又點引到你班人？<br />\n你哋唔撚做野 又點令到美國國會做野？<br />\n<br />\n唔好簽個名都懶 Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Br2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=7ca58961\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武係相輔相成 唇齒相依，上唔到前線 簽個名都可能有用。唔好話簽左無人理，係咪連打幾隻字都咁閪懶？咁你配有民主自由咩？<br />\n<br />\n最後都係嗰句:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span> 唔好咁易被人spin走，唔好人哋讓少少步就當自己贏左 可以收工"},{"pid":"ef30fb5cebe8c6f21988cfb4b784d3043b2ee711","tid":1381023,"uid":67294,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦好好玩呀?"},{"pid":"baa3c240890c19598ea531fc5ed351a5bb1742e7","tid":1381023,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Br2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e04919ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/vK4Dfno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvK4Dfno.png&h=f4f33a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXv4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXv4t.jpg&h=c2140d08&s={SIZE}\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2907faf4e26821a763f4d7afae56c594b50fc66f","tid":1381023,"uid":247845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 仲玩標題"},{"pid":"b42c1c844bfea69d1248070294a76550b0e9daa5","tid":1381023,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［重開 長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab73